{"title":"摄影师来到岛上","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"摄影师来到岛上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摄影师来到岛上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们挤在他身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像参加盛大的检阅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都打扮得整洁漂亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照相机卡卡直响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会就照好一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个新兵实在囉嗦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把摄影师也弄得没有主张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他正一正帽子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又摸一摸肩章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说皮带扎得太紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又嫌皮鞋擦得不亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要照一个全身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要突出手中的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要照上营房和花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要衬一点海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要题一行小字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“永远守卫边疆”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完了还要上色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且放大三张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙纷纷问他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗这么多干啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说一张给咱父母，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张给咱社长……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一张……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他咬咬牙决心不讲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不讲有人替他讲了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一张给黄河边上的姑娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们哈哈地大笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵脸上泛红光："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“咱们照完相啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不赶快回去站岗！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}